snippet.title: The Wild World of The Sims 3 Pets (original narration by Randall)
snippet.description: Learn more about the limited edition breeds from The Sims 3 Pets for Xbox 360 and PS3.  Treat your Sims to 10 exclusive, unique breeds, including tiger dogs and skunk cats found only in the Limited Edition. They may not be honey badgers, but they are still as fearless and crazy.  Original narration by Randall.  Available October 18, 2011.  Visit www.TheSims3.com/pets for more information!
